Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though they've been born and raised in different families,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the spiritually rich Shinobu threw a lavish garden party to show off his garish tomboy fiancée. {no idea what's hanano here, maybe reference to "of hanamura family" but that doesn't sound japanese, maybe a contraction of "hana no takai" (conceited/arrogant)}{花のじゃじゃ馬婚約者を披露(戦闘?)園遊会をしたり}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Her best friend Tamaki, who was among guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,bursts into tears as she hears that the marriage break plan isn't necessarily developing to their advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, the staunch Ushigorou{一方忠義一途のうしごろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,reports seeing Boss embarrassed and oppressed, making Ranmaru feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, however, \Nthrough a series of unforeseen happenings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,things were going great for Benio, \Nas she kept winning people over one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when she got gobsmacked by the sudden, flashy appearance of her fan club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:02:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, what kind of conclusion \Nis this escapade going to arrive to?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you finding her, Lady Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, what are you doing?{べにお様どうなさるおつもりで}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, well... You said that Ranko \Nis going to serve me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought I should start \Nby showing her my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is too flashy for my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ranko, nice to meet you.{あたしらんこ、よろしくね}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ciao!{:o}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:42.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(80,200)\c&HF1E6E4&\pos(720,140)\bord0\blur1.5\fs60\b1}Episode 12\N{\fs100}Dance! Tormented beauty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't rush me like that! \NI wanna take my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to visit a noble's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you act like nothing happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, you need to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what do you think? It suits me, right? \NLook, I even put pads on my breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot! How can you \Nkeep being so nonchalant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even disguising as a maid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea of what'll happen if that geezer unmasks you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What a wonderful room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a princess's.{まるでお姫様みたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks so cosy to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you don't wanna go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me for once!{真面目に聞いて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, what is your plan here, Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're prettier than most girls, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I changed my coiffure to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've discovered that western hairstyles suit me well.{私って意外とこういう洋髪も似合うのよね}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1915, {Taishō Era, 4th year,} curling iron\Nbecomes widely used for styling people's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This was, in other words, \Nthe pioneer of permanents.{コレすなわちパーマネントの元祖である}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I have to do this, \Nor else I won't be able...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with you.{できないもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! Then, do you mean to stay in here as a maid for the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Leave all the women's work to me!{もち！女の仕事なら任しといて}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do! Go home now! \NJust pack and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No means no!{ダメったらダメ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but, but, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you...{僕心配だったんですもの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After you didn't come back immediately, \Neven though you said you would,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,living with that handsome Shinobu \Nthat I can't hold a candle to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to worry that you'd fall for him.{もしや心を惹かれたのではないかしらと}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I could no longer stand \Nliving my days and nights in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This heartbreaking agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:20.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew away!{逃げちゃった}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked so troubled at today's banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I could no longer watch idly, \Nso I made a beeline for here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You did all that... for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, stop crying now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you hopeless child...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you start crying, \Nyou won't stop for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever met Shinobu before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I did. \NRemember that time we flew the kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He even mistook me for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And after that too.\NThere, at the pub, when you went haywire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're right... It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If he finds out, \Nwe might as well return home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Que sera, sera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you, wait a second.{君、待ちたまえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah-hey, h-hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu! Weather sure is so nice today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the weather today \Nwas no complaining material...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, this here is my new maid,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,name's Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, welcome.{ましっかり}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for you \Ndownstairs. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! \NHe didn't seem to notice.{良かった気がつかなかったみたいね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, but that trademark laugh \Ndoesn't bode well.{しかし気になる笑い上戸}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he have noticed?{気づかれたかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so...{まさか}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had, he'd have said something.{気づいたら何かいうはずでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you can still return without blowing your cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.{そんなこと不可能よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you even imagine \Nwhat'll happen if the Count notices?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?{何よ今のは}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent!{お見事}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I praise him?{どうして褒めちゃいけないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to mind your place here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If he loses his nerve, he'll cut you in half with one fell swoop just like that bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so because you don't know him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really don't want to get skewered again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a problem for the future me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, you came here with\Nthe mission of breaking off the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If they unmask me, that'll just make it easier for us to pack up and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And they can kiss our butts goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, I've mastered a lot of women's roles in my early days of training to be an actor. {no idea what's the "when the oumihattoi was born" part}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave all the misleading \Nto my impeccable acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, it's as Ranmaru says.{それは蘭丸の言う通りですぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If we three join our strengths,\Nwe can make a mess of this house in no time!{このうちを引っ掻き回してやろうじゃねえですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it? And even if they find out, \Nwe'll just take our leave then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what'll likely happen instead, is you'd be begging Count for forgiveness when he finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're worrying too much about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment...
