Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.06,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\move(1685,360,700,360,000,700)\c&H21201B&\3c&H79A6B4&}Gentlemen{殿方}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.06,0:09:33.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\move(700,360,1685,360,000,400)\c&H21201B&\3c&H79A6B4&}Gentlemen{殿方}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio! Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-I got it, I got it, I got it.{わかったわかったわかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to go the other way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw right through me, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:12.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1400)\blur1\c&H2C253D&\3c&H6A8AA6&\pos(751.61,76)\frz358.8}Gentlemen{殿方}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. And what happened next?{そうかなるほどそれで}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Takayashiki returning to the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I saw Tamaki all the way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but she still was noticeably \Ndeeply dispirited by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well, let's drink.{まあいいから飲め}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.02,0:10:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.{ありがとう}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, Shinobu, where's Benio, \Nthe star of the party?{おい少尉パーティーの主役のべにおさんはどうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be back soon. A new maid came, \Nso she's showing her around.{新しいメイドが来たのでちょっと取り込んでるんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, that training must've been exhausting. {lit: made you sweat}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you perhaps like a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?{そっちは}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ranko, the newest addition to your maids, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who clapped earlier, right?{宣告手を叩いたのはその方か}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so outstandingly spectacular, I couldn't help but lose my bearings in the most inappropriate manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.\NUnlike most of your peers these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you've demonstrated \Nan admirable respect for martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes, that look...\ND-Did he find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty lady, pretty lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From today onward, you're my personal aide. \NOnly cater to my orders and needs. Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to forgive her fit of impropriety. \NRanko is Benio's personal maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Too early to relax just yet! \NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name's Ranko, isn't it?{蘭子とか申したな}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you serve Benio now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, I don't like where this is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you come from?\NWho's your guarantor? {身元引受人は誰じゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't need to interrogate her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.33,Overlap,,0,0,0,,No, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never dealt with common folk so you don't know, \Nbut the make-believe fraudsters are aplenty these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know full well \Nabout those make-believe fraudsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They get hired in rich families and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,use their assumed personalities to rob said families blind, never to be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, Ranm-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, erm, I mean, Ranko \Nwould never be implicated in such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And her guarantor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou from Kurumahiki Clan!{車引きのうしごろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...And that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, our two families have always been close, \Nso your suspicions are groundless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a dude disguising as a girl. \NWho'd ever call me suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, was she sent here by your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what can our new friend do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir. As a woman, I know more or less about every part of the housework,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.19,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but cooking is definitely my forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's your special dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your special dish, say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear! Enough of this farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Benio's family deemed her worthy of being sent here, she has to be a very capable individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your special dish, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I know, it's the boiled potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boiled potatoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it. {lit is "can"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you just saying that\Nto mock my Satsuma origins,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and my samurai prowess?! {その方を薩摩出身と承知の上で - this is because 薩摩芋 - satsumaimo - is sweet potato, how could I put\Nit though. Alternative: you said this because they make potatoes in my birthplace; 芋侍と苦労いたしが - another pun,芋侍 means boorish samurai}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is potato a forbidden product in your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Insolent brat, you just can't stop \Ntalking back, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,En garde!{覚悟}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Count! Ranko knows nothing \Nabout you and your origins! {お爺様! らんこはお爺様の出身地も何も知らないのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, lower that katana.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.52,0:14:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My sixth sense just can't \Nstop detecting something fishy about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was thanks to my unfaltering sixth sense that I \Nweathered and survived the Meiji Restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have fooled others, \Nbut I can see right through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it. I definitely feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be some other thing that you excel at.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare hiding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What he means is... \NAre you familiar with any of the traditional arts?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I know a bit of traditional dance.{はい日本舞踊をいささか}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's possible. \NSo what is your school?{して流派は}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujieda school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Fujieda school, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. As a matter of fact, I'm the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're the head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I meant to say the head himself \Nappointed me an accredited master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A master at that age?{その若さで名取か}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, she's been practicing since she was this small, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A dancing master is just what we need,\Nas today is the day we're holding a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dance will entertain our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A dance would prove invaluable \Nto adorn the celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, she was only \Npromised an accreditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You may find yourself severely unimpressed by it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for modesty. Wife, make arrangements for the costumes and stage to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, I also think we're asking for too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, since we're holding an introduction party for Benio today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,it befits us to provide an elegant display to everything she brought with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:13.43,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:21.44,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:28.32,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:42.75,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:56.10,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:17:02.40,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:13.10,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. That was not half-bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The performer is the founder of the Fujieda School
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,young kabuki actor Fujieda Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.90,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This had suddenly took a turn for worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? So she's the head herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, would you care to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes! W-Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujieda Ranmaru... Isn't that a male name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain yourself, or else... {no idea what's rentou here}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! This is turning into a disaster! \NI have to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,O-ho! Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I can just play along! {not a single word}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, please forgive me.{お爺様お許しを}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Her being the dance school master Fujieda Ranmaru was a fabrication all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl was so lucky as to have a face that resembles Fujieda Ranmaru's,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of that, \Nshe was born with a gift for dancing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And even her name is Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking after Fujieda Ranmaru \Nis a nasty habit she just can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like two peas in a pod, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to dispel your doubts \Nhere and now, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Still clinging to that bad habit of yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You like to feel yourself Fujieda Ranmaru so much, \Nyou'd even deceive others for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot-idiot-idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, idiot-idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.65,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Count had decided to overlook your slip-up today, if you promise to reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he catches you returning to your old ways ever again, you're getting a taste of his katana,\Nso better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks to me like her determination is firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko, you can start with your duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how a certain day of a certain month of 1918 was concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:47.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs10\t(0,2400,\fs70)\fade(350,0)\pos(735,120)\c&H152218&\3c&H24C3DE&}Good job, {\c&H2525C8&}Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio, the bathroom \Nis prepared for your use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you, Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to enter the bath with Lady Benio and rub her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that a joke, Mrs. Kisaragi?{今なんか冗談言ったきさらぎさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the custom for high-ranking \Nladies of noble families
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave the matters of bathing and such to their court ladies. {lit: lavatory and all such things}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get naked and bathe with her!{あなたも裸になって共に入るのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Start undoing your clothing. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ranmaru is literally( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's there to be so embarrassed about? \NAll our maids are females too, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... B-But not all of them! \NRanko is actually a ma—{違うんだったらその蘭子は}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"A ma?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "a ma?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean, you're a ma-ature person, \Nso we find it embarrassing to undress before you. {lit: adult, so ... - maybe meaning you're less conscious about it when youre a child, but then kisaragi leaves so I guess she talks about her after all}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right! That's exactly the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come see you two later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tee-hee-hee.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She may insist all she wants, \Nbut we won't bathe together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.69,0:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you sneak out and hide somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not like your skin and bones \Ninterest me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know it's skin and bones \Nif you haven't seen it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always so rough with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.04,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew something like this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you neglect your duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I lost my cool for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I let him see my shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she finally accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.61,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the frying pan into the fire,{一難去ってまた一難}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy and a girl are forced \Nto bathe together.{男女一緒に風呂に入れとは}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the warm waters of our springs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will the flowers bloom or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio can't help but worry \Nthat Ranmaru's true cross-dressing identity{男女の蘭丸の正体がいつバレるかと}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,might be unveiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Ranmaru and Ushigorou \Nlive without a care in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.97,0:23:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, chaos and commotion ensue.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:11.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,Boss Hanamura Benio's Dwelling{https://www.weblio.jp/content/%E5%BE%A1%E5%AE%BF%E6%89%80/花村紅緒親分御宿所; unsure about 御 character - pere}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The ruthless drilling instructor \Nis finally knocked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but even so, \NShinobu uncovers Ranmaru's disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.05,0:23:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on "Here Comes the High Collar Lady":\NLove is a Sailboat of Reflection.{恋は思案の帆掛け船}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
